headline: Q4 Earnings Outperformers: Hologic (NASDAQ:HOLX) And The Rest Of The Medical Devices & Supplies - Imaging, Diagnostics Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how medical devices & supplies - imaging, diagnostics stocks fared in Q4, starting with Hologic (NASDAQ:HOLX).
